{"tid":207763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首季電騙損失逾4000萬 警方：一半個案都是假冒官員","createTime":"2017-04-19T05:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T05:45:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27a710bdb9f56314b21fb42a8a5db85db3c86cad","tid":207763,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"假冒內地官員的電話騙案未有遏止，最新便有一名26歲港大內地女生遇上電話騙徒，遭騙走約71萬元人民幣。警方表示電話騙案有上升趨勢，單在復活節便有11宗假冒官員的案件，涉及款項1245萬元，當中4宗案件分別各損失超過100萬元。<br />\n<br />\n東九龍總區重案組總督察譚威信今早在記者會上表示，今年3、4月的電話騙案個案較今年1、2月明顯上升，而今年首季共接獲171宗電話騙案，當中127宗有損失，涉款超過4000萬元，當中超過一半個案都是假冒官員。<br />\n<br />\n譚威信指假冒官員的騙案萬變不離其宗，騙徒都是指受害人干犯罪行，要求受害人將保證金存入銀行，其間套取銀行密碼，再將受害人的錢取走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56583478&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56583478%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170419&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=714b236b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56583478%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170419&h=b87f8af8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56583478&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170419</a>"},{"pid":"6e759dba774a6c07b83db2797088770f51002577","tid":207763,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:43:22.000Z","msg":"新大茶飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a8782c4441637bc7a34c876ab4057c383d992c","tid":207763,"uid":16380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:44:44.000Z","msg":"另一半真係官員?"},{"pid":"83dabe9165a50421c109578856c635cf2f80555f","tid":207763,"uid":64225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"葉繼歡都激死<br />\n<br />\n咁辛苦揸槍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}